DATA PRIVACY NOTICE
================================================================================

This software stores data locally in the user's home directory (~/.skillrunner/).
Data collected includes:
- Imported skills and agents
- Usage metrics and execution logs
- Model performance statistics
- Configuration settings
- Cached execution results

No data is transmitted to JBC Tech Solutions or any third party except:
- When explicitly configured to use cloud LLM APIs (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google)
- API requests are sent directly to the configured provider

For more information, see PRIVACY.md

